/home/agent/shipyard-ai/prds/parked/daemon-fix-watcher-skip-loop.parked-superseded.md:The two filters disagree on what "already processed" means. Bring them into agreement: a PRD is **NOT** already processed if a fresh copy in `prds/` exists with mtime **newer** than any copy in `failed/` or `parked/`. (`completed/` always wins — never re-attempt a shipped PRD.)
